{"tid":1486764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性]講暴力退潮係暗煽動暴力升級","createTime":"2019-08-19T03:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T03:40:04.000Z","uid":271668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"56f2c9ccc622e1fc4918e4cb7a7a4a913c83429a","tid":1486764,"uid":271668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:37:22.000Z","msg":"P仔大膽開個post回應，預左被人插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇咗幾個post講818，手足們傾行動之前不如諗諗，唔係阻你做，而家大陸好多蠱惑招，唔想大家白白犧牲，如果諗清楚就去做！！！<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">永遠支持！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">-唔好為咗證明自己唔係乜嘢而特登做啲乜嘢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">-知己知彼百戰百勝</span></span><br />\n講計謀我哋永遠唔及中共咁蠱惑，所以我哋更加要小心唔好淨係睇表面講咗啲乜嘢，派啲大陸人落單被人玩就係一個好好嘅例子<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">-我哋嘅敵人係公狗黑</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋嘅戰友係真香港人</span></span><br />\n敵人好強勁，我哋更加要穩定軍心，意思其實同上面差唔多，唔好被分化，唔好被煽動，香港人最叻就係靈活變動、見招拆招，面對咁強大嘅敵人，正面對敵無得玩，暫時見到玩流水、街坊落場都係班狗未拆到嘅方法，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">欣賞大家好醒目，期待更多有創意嘅方法</span>[size=4]<br />\n<br />\n我好想支持先出個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係想屌唔係想割，呢場仗犧牲在所難免，但係都要犧牲得有價值有意義，<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔想手足再白白犧牲受苦</span></span><br />\n[size=4]<span style=\"color: navy;\">見到你哋比狗打到咁我個心好痛</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求下你哋理性同衝動要平衡</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"e17d7e586ac5ae3642d51c5986ec0eef141b0c10","tid":1486764,"uid":271668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:40:04.000Z","msg":"對唔住啲色同字體大小亂9晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}